<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Re: Roleplaying a pvp</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Biggest_Loser">Biggest_Loser</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 3:25 a.m. 26/12/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Re: Roleplaying a pvp<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=2361" TARGET=_self>Roleplaying a pvp</A> (Bragador)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>> Hi,

<BR>&gt; I just want to say that pvp is a must in a virtual world like
<BR>&gt; everquest. Without pvp, there would be no bounty hunters, no
<BR>&gt; criminals that attack the road travellers, etc. AND there would
<BR>&gt; be no raid against cities!
<BR>&gt; The problem is that some pk can't roleplay a fun caracter and
<BR>&gt; they just run around trying to kill evreyone that can't resist
<BR>&gt; their wrath. Those are missing a great part of the game. And i'm
<BR>&gt; no talking about those who wait next to the corpses of their
<BR>&gt; victims to kill them 3-4 times.
<BR>&gt; I would like that we, fellow pk, starts a new way of playing,
<BR>&gt; the way of the futur. Let us live our caracter without having to
<BR>&gt; encounter serial killers every 5 minutes. Show the example and
<BR>&gt; roleplay your caracter(by roleplaying I don't mean speaking in
<BR>&gt; old english, i'm speaking about acting in a realistic way).
<BR>&gt; Remember this: pkilling is not a excuse to make everquest a huge
<BR>&gt; brawling game, it's suppose to add realism. Instead of saying
<BR>&gt; hail to whoever you meet, pkilling makes us act in a realistic
<BR>&gt; manner saying : stop! who's there? what do you want?.
<BR>&gt; I hope someday pkilling will be realistic and not like what it
<BR>&gt; is today.
<BR>&gt; Because saying that some races, or even some classes are not
<BR>&gt; appropriate for a pk world is a very very very sad proof that
<BR>&gt; the fun of being a pk is reducing. IT IS NOT A COMBAT ARENA,
<BR>&gt; IT'S AN ADVENTURE GAME WITH EVIL CARACTERS IN IT. (by the way,
<BR>&gt; don't forget you can be a pk AND a good caracter ex:shadow
<BR>&gt; knight vs paladin)
<P>&gt; SO roleplay, don't kill everyone you see.
<P>&gt; Bragador
<P>RPG Player Killing is not as fun as PURE PKing 3D shooters like Sin, Quake 3, and hundreds of other PK internet first person shooters. All carnage bay-bee!
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
